<i>Causal Independence for Probability Assessment and Inference Using Bayesian Networks</i>.</a>
<li>Boutilier, Friedman, Goldszmidt &amp; Koller, <a href="http://www.cs.ucla.edu/~darwiche/cs262a/bfgk_csi_uai96.ps">
<i>Context-Specific Independence in Bayesian Networks</i>.</a>
<li>Dechter, <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~csp/R48a.ps">
<i>Bucket Elimination: A Unifying Framework for Probabilistic Inference</i>.</a>
